data.description:
This is a legacy release of Big Time Color for those who have chosen to retain their Pebble's 3.0 firmware and not upgrade to 4.0.  

Big Time Color is an expansion of Pebble's original Big Time, their easiest-to-read digital face, with these additional configurable features:
1. An optional analog second hand (we know how useful they can be);
2. An optional date and two-week calendar, which appears upon wrist shake (duration is configurable);
3. An optional battery indicator; and
4. An optional Bluetooth-connection icon to alert you if your watch has disconnected from your phone (yes, it'll vibrate on disconnect/reconnect).
